  "title": "Administrative Assistant/Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>KIAT LEE LANDSCAPE & BUILDING PTE LTD</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will perform data entry, procurement support, document filing, and scanning tasks to ensure smooth office operations. You will also handle other assigned duties to support the team’s daily functions.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Enter data accurately into company systems to maintain up-to-date records</li><li>Manage procurement tasks by processing purchase requests and coordinating with suppliers to support timely acquisitions</li><li>Organize and file documents systematically to enable easy retrieval and maintain office order</li><li>Scan documents efficiently to create digital copies for record-keeping and sharing</li><li>Complete assigned ad hoc duties promptly to support team needs and operational efficiency</li><li>Meet deadlines consistently to ensure smooth workflow and project progress</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>GCE O level, ITE, or Diploma qualification with 1 to 2 years of relevant work experience</li><li>Ability to organize work and pay close attention to detail</li><li>Availability to start work on short notice</li><li>Willingness to work a 5-day work week</li></ul>",
